===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  stream_supports_lock ( resource $stream ) : bool~

Tells whether the stream supports locking through |flock|.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{stream}

  The stream to check.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Returns TRUE on success or FALSE on failure.

